metadata.name: Slumber Bunny
metadata.description:
A conceptual self-portrait curated to create a feeling of sleepiness. This is achieved by adding the expressions of a yawn. As an artist, I get really motivated while showcasing natural day-to-day human emotions in my portraits. The small details of human nature matter to me a lot and I always try to inculcate this in my photography. Hope you didnâ€™t yawn back !

Editions : 30
